## PHASE VF-7 — Footer Logo & Social Placeholder

**Goal:** The footer currently shows only a text wordmark and a generic "Follow for pop-up announcements" line with no social link. Add the logo mark and wire up the Instagram link from the Customizer setting.

**Cursor Prompt:**

Open `template-parts/footer/footer-content.php` (or equivalent).

**1. Replace the text-only logo with the actual logo image:**
```php
<div class="footer__brand">
  <a href="<?php echo esc_url( home_url( '/' ) ); ?>">
    <img
      src="<?php echo esc_url( get_theme_file_uri( 'reference-images/logo-primary.png' ) ); ?>"
      alt="<?php bloginfo( 'name' ); ?>"
      class="footer__logo"
      width="120"
      height="120"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </a>
  <p class="footer__tagline">Pop-up BBQ. Sell-out quality.</p>
</div>
```

**2. Wire Instagram link from Customizer:**
```php
<?php
$instagram_url = get_theme_mod( 'jjbbq_instagram_url', '' );
if ( $instagram_url ) : ?>
  <a
    href="<?php echo esc_url( $instagram_url ); ?>"
    class="footer__social-link"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    aria-label="Follow Jorkin' Joel's on Instagram"
  >
    Follow the Smoke on Instagram ↗
  </a>
<?php endif; ?>
```

**3. Footer logo sizing:**
```scss
.footer__logo {
  width: 120px;
  height: auto;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3));
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.footer__tagline {
  font-family: $font-body;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}

.footer__social-link {
  font-family: $font-display;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: $color-gold;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  transition: color 0.15s ease;

  &:hover {
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
}
```

